This rich dataset unveils the intricacies of Nike's sales performance within the crucial US market.  Empower your business analyses with:

Historical Sales Trends: Gain insights into Nike's sales performance over time, identifying seasonal fluctuations, product category dominance, and potential market shifts.
Geographic Performance: Analyze sales data across different US regions, uncovering variations in customer preferences and purchase patterns.
Product-Level Analysis: Delve into the performance of individual products or categories, understanding which items resonate most with US consumers.
